title: Kyland Young of 'Big Brother' on His ‘Challenge: USA’ Experience | Death, Taxes, and Bananas
description:
Johnny is joined this week by Kyland Young from ‘Big Brother’ Season 23 and ‘The Challenge: USA’ after his shocking elimination in Episode 7. They chat about how he got into the reality television space, his breakout performance on ‘Big Brother’ Season 23 and his involvement in the Cookout alliance, his dominant showing on ‘The Challenge: USA,’ and much more.
Host: Johnny Bananas
Guest: Kyland Young
Producer: Sasha Ashall
